## 3. Sequential Questions

- Only one question at a time
- Each question should build on previous answers
- Wait for response before proceeding

## 4. Language Standards

- **Communication**: Spanish or English for convenience
- **All Technical Artifacts in English**:
  - Code (variables, functions, classes)
  - Documentation
  - Git commit messages
  - Test names and descriptions
  - Configuration files

